Package: polyfreq
Type: Package
Title: Fast De Silva Allele Frequency Estimation for Polyploids
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Author", "Name", email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an optimized pure-R implementation of the de Silva et al.
    (2005) EM algorithm for estimating allele frequencies in polyploid populations
    under polysomic inheritance with a mixed mating system (selfing + random
    mating). All subroutines previously compiled in C/C++ within the 'polysat'
    package are re-implemented using vectorized R operations and sparse-matrix
    algebra. Uses the 'genambig' class and accessor functions from 'polysat'.
    Reference: De Silva HN, Hall AJ, Rikkerink E, McNeilage MA, Fraser LG (2005)
    <doi:10.1038/sj.hdy.6800728>.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    cli,
    future,
    future.apply,
    Matrix,
    polysat,
    Rcpp
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
